{"type": "article", "id": 19555, "title": "“M+D拐杖”", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-23T07:37:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606140500J0uFbPp6zUh1Ylmq.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这对“M+D拐杖”是绕在胳膊上的，来自美国的设计团队 Mobility Designed。他们想要改变传统的拐杖夹在腋窝下的使用习惯，拐杖的上面用两根很灵活的臂环固定，让拐杖根据手臂的摆动而移动，使行走更轻松。此外，它有可替换的防滑脚套，方便长期使用。单个售价 100 美元，<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/682596326/m-d-crutches-painfree-stylish-and-custom-elbow-cru\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150027WriZkqgLDPsMwYXe.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150027zVfChdYeUxl6sN7P.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"450\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.41666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261500284jOEJxAoNQZPg9KD.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"534\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.49444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150028LGUJu6T1bCHXmWov.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"731\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.89364303\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}